There are two main issues with your code:

- When you pass an `Integer` to `List#remove`, it&#39;s using the overload that removes an element by value (see [`List#remove(Object)`](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/19/docs/api/java.base/java/util/List.html#remove(java.lang.Object))). You would need to pass an `int` instead to remove by **index**.
- In order to delete elements while iterating, to avoid skipping elements, you should either loop backwards or use an `Iterator`.

